.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558172&idx=1&sn=4352d94bba884ceac8f3f231a9074910","date":"2026-02-03 00:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_bc19b98b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":42,"score":93},{"id":"RAW_df4d1702","title":"生产级 Prompt 自动化推理评估 A/B 实验结果的工程实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558131&idx=1&sn=73317842c9c513c3bde07efac9cee952","date":"2026-02-02 00:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_df4d1702.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":95,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_3f0cd641","title":"刚刚，ChatGPT 和 Claude 同时大更新，不会给 AI 当老板的打工人要被淘汰","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654369?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-06 06:26:22","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3f0cd641.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":11,"score":82},{"id":"RAW_02f3485c","title":"闭门探讨：130 位 AI 创业者，对 Clawdbot 和下一代 AI 产品的 39 条思考","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg5NTc0MjgwMw==&mid=2247522622&idx=1&sn=915a298b9821ae8d3205f9044a6a6060","date":"2026-02-05 11:36:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文汇总了 130 位 AI 创业者对 Clawdbot（OpenClaw）的深度思考，探讨了 Agent 自我进化、Skill 替代 App、A2A 互动及安全挑战等前沿趋势。","summary":"文章整理自 Founder Park 举办的 AI 创业者闭门会，核心围绕现象级开源 Agent 项目 Clawdbot 展开。与会者认为，Clawdbot 的突破在于赋予了 AI 极高的自主权限，使其能够通过编辑和创造 Skill 实现自我进化。未来，AI 的交互范式将发生根本性变革：IM（即时通讯）将成为新的 OS，而 Skill 将取代 App 成为核心能力单元。讨论还深入到了「存储即文件系统」的记忆机制，并提出 AI 发展的终极形态是 AI 与 AI 之间的（A2A）高速互动，而非受限于人类带宽的 H2A 模式。同时，专家们也警示了当前在安全沙箱、Token 成本及文件检索效率方面的严重短板。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_02f3485c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Founder Park","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":92},{"id":"RAW_c5ad6994","title":"10 万 Agent 在 Moltbook 娱乐空谈，小冰之父出手造了个生产力实干版","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376802.html","date":"2026-02-06 02:39:07","oneSentenceSummary":"“小冰之父”李笛创立的 Nextie 发布多智能体平台“团子”，通过混合型 MAS 架构实现 Agent 间的辩论与投票，将群体智能从娱乐转向生产力实干。","summary":"本文介绍了由原微软小冰核心团队创立的 Nextie 公司及其新产品“团子”。文章对比了近期火爆但偏向娱乐的 Moltbook，强调“团子”致力于利用群体智能解决复杂的现实生产力问题。该平台通过搭建具备深度思辨和对抗性辩论机制的 Agent 协作体系，让不同专业背景的智能体针对用户问题进行拆解、博弈并投票表决。技术上，Nextie 采用了混合型多智能体架构（Hybrid MAS），旨在将“思考方式”与“领域知识”解耦，通过思考过程透明化和认知平权，显著降低单点决策偏差。实验数据显示，该方法在复杂决策任务上的智能深度优于部分顶级单一大模型，且能有效降低计算消耗。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c5ad6994.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":23,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_9f4cc823","title":"Mitchell Hashimoto：我的 AI 采用之旅","link":"https://simonwillison.net/2026/Feb/5/ai-adoption-journey/#atom-everything","date":"2026-02-05 23:39:07","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9f4cc823.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Simon Willison's Weblog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":1,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_9f824261","title":"邓明扬一作论文改写生成范式！何恺明也署名了","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376752.html","date":"2026-02-05 15:26:57","oneSentenceSummary":"何恺明团队提出“漂移模型”（Drifting Models），通过将分布演化从推理阶段转移至训练阶段，实现了高质量的单步图像生成。","summary":"文章详细介绍了由邓明扬（一作）、何恺明等人提出的全新生成模型范式——漂移模型。该模型的核心创新在于引入“漂移场”机制，将传统扩散模型或流匹配模型在推理时的多步迭代过程，转化为神经网络训练过程中的自然演化。通过在训练中直接对齐先验分布与真实数据分布，漂移模型在 ImageNet 256×256 基准测试中仅需单步推理（1-NFE）即可达到 1.54 FID 的顶尖水平，性能媲美甚至超越了需要数百步迭代的传统模型。此外，该范式在具身智能控制任务中也展现出极低的延迟和极强的性能，为实时 AI 应用提供了新路径。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9f824261.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_84866bf0","title":"面壁智能开源全模态模型 MiniCPM-o4.5，边看边听还能主动抢答","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376714.html","date":"2026-02-05 15:19:59","oneSentenceSummary":"面壁智能开源 MiniCPM-o4.5 全模态模型，通过全双工实时流机制实现边看边听、主动应答的端侧 AI 交互新范式。","summary":"文章详细介绍了面壁智能最新开源的 9B 参数全模态模型 MiniCPM-o4.5。该模型突破了传统 AI 的“回合制”问答模式，引入全双工多模态实时流机制，支持模型在输出的同时持续接收视听输入，实现即时打断和主动提醒。技术上，模型通过文本与语音 Token 交错建模及流式编解码器重构，解决了 I/O 阻塞问题。面壁智能强调“软硬一体”的端侧路线，通过与芯片厂商深度协同，旨在将该模型应用于具身智能、智能座舱及各类 AI 硬件（如松果派开发板），推动 AI 从“问答机”向“全天候伴随助手”转型。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_84866bf0.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":16,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_473dec97","title":"谷歌北大联手学术版 Banana 爆火，论文图表 100%精确生成","link":"https://www.qbitai.com/2026/02/376451.html","date":"2026-02-05 06:15:38","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_473dec97.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"量子位","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_05bfeee1","title":"退隐 3 年后回归，周末写的 AI 一夜刷屏、一周拿下 10 万 Star 增速超 Linux，Clawdbot 之父首次长谈：如今几乎不看自己发布的代码","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg4NDQwNTI0OQ==&mid=2247588728&idx=1&sn=042881f37d34969c3b08f85ddbb23cbf","date":"2026-02-04 10:02:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_05bfeee1.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"AI科技大本营","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":99,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_c347f932","title":"文本生成图像模型训练设计：消融实验的经验教训","link":"https://huggingface.co/blog/Photoroom/prx-part2","date":"2026-02-03 11:25:53","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c347f932.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"Hugging Face Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_6dbd507b","title":"今日开源（2026-2-2）：阶跃智能 Step-3.5-Flash 系列上线，199B 基座+FP8/Int4 量化技术，压缩优化赋能低开销多硬件 NLP 部署","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247501528&idx=1&sn=d4a1cacb26e74cdf45aa3055ca563728","date":"2026-02-02 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_6dbd507b.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Artificial_Intelligence","sourceName":"机器之心SOTA模型","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f9ebd09d","title":"【第 3655 期】浏览器即运行时：一个零后端 AI 应用的前端架构实践","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278596&idx=1&sn=dea55dba00065e03f83445a08be9f33e","date":"2026-02-06 01:03:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文探讨了如何利用 WebLLM、Yjs 和 WebGPU 等前沿技术，构建一个完全在浏览器端运行、零后端、隐私优先的 AI 财富规划系统架构。","summary":"文章详细介绍了名为 Meridian 的财富规划平台的架构实践，提出“浏览器即运行时”模式。作者通过 WebLLM 在浏览器端直接运行量化的 Llama 3.2 模型实现边缘 AI 推理，利用 Yjs 和 IndexedDB 构建本地优先（Local-first）的分布式状态管理系统，并使用 React Three Fiber 结合 WebGPU 进行高性能金融数据可视化。该架构旨在解决金融数据隐私、云端计算成本和 API 延迟问题，同时也客观分析了模型下载冷启动和硬件依赖等必然的权衡，展示了“主权云”应用的新范式。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f9ebd09d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"前端早读课","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":83},{"id":"RAW_8262b259","title":"告别“伪智能”代码：用 Spec + RAG 打造真正懂你的 AI 程序员","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzOTU0NTQ0MA==&mid=2247558194&idx=1&sn=ece018ca2921b2d51176c37a91bd23f3","date":"2026-02-06 00:32:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8262b259.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"阿里云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":43,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_827ad3e6","title":"为什么你的 UI 不更新：调试 React 应用中的陈旧数据和缓存问题","link":"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/why-your-ui-wont-update-debugging-stale-data-and-caching-in-react-apps/","date":"2026-02-05 17:32:01","oneSentenceSummary":"一份通过系统地调试五个缓存层和本地状态陷阱，来识别并解决 React 应用中 UI 数据陈旧问题的全面指南。","summary":"本文针对开发者经常遇到的困扰——尽管数据修改成功，但 React UI 却未能更新的问题进行了探讨。文章引入了一个结构化的思维模型，通过识别五个不同的缓存层（React Query 客户端缓存、Next.js fetch 服务端缓存、浏览器 HTTP 缓存、CDN/托管缓存以及 Service Workers），帮助开发者摆脱“凭直觉猜测”的困境。作者还强调了一个常见的“非缓存”陷阱，即重复的 React 本地状态。针对每一层，指南都提供了具体的症状、“快速检查”调试技巧（如检查 DevTools 网络请求头或使用缓存清除查询参数）以及代码层面的解决方案（如显式缓存失效和设置 “no-store” 策略）。最后，文章提供了一个“10 秒调试指南”，帮助开发者根据网络请求行为快速定位问题层。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_827ad3e6.json","topicTag":"frontend-fullstack","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"freeCodeCamp.org","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":10,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_f15666e2","title":"带爪子的机器人","link":"https://world.hey.com/dhh/clankers-with-claws-9f86fa71","date":"2026-02-05 15:30:07","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f15666e2.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"David Heinemeier Hansson","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_ccc5aae0","title":"2025 年第四季度 DDoS 威胁报告：创纪录的 31.4 Tbps 攻击为大规模 DDoS 攻击之年画上句号","link":"https://blog.cloudflare.com/ddos-threat-report-2025-q4/","date":"2026-02-05 14:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"Cloudflare 2025 年第四季度报告详述了 DDoS 攻击创纪录的一年，重点提及了 31.4 Tbps 的攻击以及 Aisuru-Kimwolf Android TV 僵尸网络的兴起。","summary":"第 24 版 Cloudflare DDoS 威胁报告显示，2025 年攻击量激增 121%，共拦截 4710 万次事件。第四季度主要受“圣诞前夜”行动主导，其中由多达 400 万台受感染 Android TV 组成的 Aisuru-Kimwolf 僵尸网络发起了峰值达每秒 2.05 亿次请求 (Mrps) 的超大规模 HTTP 攻击。一项新的世界纪录由一次持续仅 35 秒的 31.4 Tbps 攻击创下。报告指出攻击目标发生了转移，电信行业成为受攻击最多的行业，地理分布也出现显著变化，包括英国和香港的排名上升。此外，报告指出由于虚拟机易于配置，云计算平台已成为攻击流量的主要来源。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ccc5aae0.json","topicTag":"devops","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The Cloudflare Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":7,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_2c039aeb","title":"从测试驱动开发和生产环境测试中获取反馈","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/feedback-TDD-production/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-05 11:36:00","oneSentenceSummary":"本文提倡一种高速开发工作流，通过 TDD、结对编程和生产环境测试来取代传统的预发布环境和端到端测试。","summary":"本文基于 QCon London 的演讲，详细介绍了一种优先考虑快速反馈循环的成熟工程方法论。作者认为，传统的端到端 (E2E) 测试和预发布环境往往是对现实的拙劣模拟，存在数据质量问题和冗长的供应环节。相反，他们提出了一种模型，让团队依赖于通过 TDD 和结对编程开发的健壮单元测试和集成测试。通过将 TDD 视为设计工具而非仅仅是测试工具，团队可以实现更好的模块化和更低的耦合。通过使用特性开关 (Feature Toggles) 和频繁的小规模部署，在生产环境中管理风险。这种经过十年磨炼的方法强调，最高质量的反馈直接来自生产环境，使团队能够更精准地导航和转型。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2c039aeb.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_f53152a5","title":"持续 AI 实践：开发者今天如何利用智能体 CI 实现自动化","link":"https://github.blog/ai-and-ml/generative-ai/continuous-ai-in-practice-what-developers-can-automate-today-with-agentic-ci/","date":"2026-02-05 09:00:00","oneSentenceSummary":"GitHub Next 推出“持续 AI”，这是一种利用智能体推理来自动化处理传统确定性 CI 无法应对的重判断工程任务的范式。","summary":"本文探讨了软件自动化从基于规则的持续集成（CI）向基于推理的“持续 AI”的演进。虽然传统 CI 擅长测试和构建等确定性任务，但在处理需要判断的任务时（如识别文档与代码不匹配或检测细微的性能回归）却力不从心。GitHub Next 提出了一种模式，即后台智能体在代码库中运行，利用自然语言规则处理这些“高认知负担”的杂务。该方法的核心是“安全输出”框架，确保智能体在严格的权限下运行，生成 Pull Request 等可审查的产物，而非自主提交代码。实际实验显示了显著的收益，例如以极低的成本将测试覆盖率从 5% 提高到 100%，这预示着未来代码库将托管一系列专门的智能体来持续维护代码质量。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f53152a5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The GitHub Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_53038dfa","title":"一次大文件处理性能优化实录","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&mid=2650542848&idx=1&sn=182f2cc442bb91d9e6db18d2e28bd403","date":"2026-02-04 09:29:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_53038dfa.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":38,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_28e7cf74","title":"百度沧海·存储 Mantle 系统架构演进之路，SOSP'25 论文背后的故事","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651274349&idx=3&sn=497e917454ddfc7d2572bd8c7a258f16","date":"2026-02-04 05:31:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_28e7cf74.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ 中文","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":62,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_c1c30c76","title":"用 Go 重构 C++老系统，一次降本 82%的极致之旅","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI2NDU4OTExOQ==&mid=2247694348&idx=1&sn=9e955e9aec449ec3245339142575cd1e","date":"2026-02-04 00:46:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_c1c30c76.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"腾讯云开发者","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":12,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_9661d297","title":"【第 3653 期】一个 CLAUDE.md，让 AI 真正懂你的项目：从配置到长期提效的完整指南","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MTA1MjAxMQ==&mid=2651278571&idx=1&sn=66e4f199ff6c325a9415c9c4bf3dcaad","date":"2026-02-03 01:01:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9661d297.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"前端早读课","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":17,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_9bee791b","title":"视频超分与补帧框架，AI 驱动画质流畅升级 | 开源日报 No.870","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2NTk2OTM2OA==&mid=2247494014&idx=1&sn=42fc8f26ea2a193dc6bdb5317a96b45c","date":"2026-02-03 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9bee791b.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"开源服务指南","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_3b1268ec","title":"AI 风险管理：保障 AI 系统安全的全面指南","link":"https://www.databricks.com/blog/ai-risk-management-comprehensive-guide-securing-ai-systems","date":"2026-02-02 21:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3b1268ec.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Databricks","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":8,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_64acd644","title":"晋升总监：规模化至 100 人以上工程团队的经验教训","link":"https://www.infoq.com/presentations/patterns-organizational-change/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-02 16:23:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_64acd644.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_5aad67d8","title":"MemAlign：利用可扩展记忆从人类反馈中构建更好的 LLM 裁判","link":"https://www.databricks.com/blog/memalign-building-better-llm-judges-human-feedback-scalable-memory","date":"2026-02-02 15:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_5aad67d8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"Databricks","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":9,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_a38759cf","title":"Airbnb 通过 “Pay as a Local” 扩展全球结账功能，在 14 个月内覆盖 220 个市场","link":"https://www.infoq.com/news/2026/02/airbnb-global-payaslocal/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-02 15:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_a38759cf.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":3,"score":85},{"id":"RAW_d0573b76","title":"Koog x ACP：将智能体连接到你的 IDE 及更多平台 | JetBrains AI 博客","link":"https://blog.jetbrains.com/ai/2026/02/koog-x-acp-connect-an-agent-to-your-ide-and-more/","date":"2026-02-02 13:02:34","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d0573b76.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"The JetBrains Blog","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":5,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_776188f5","title":"为什么大多数机器学习项目无法投入生产","link":"https://www.infoq.com/articles/why-ml-projects-fail-production/?utm_campaign=infoq_content&utm_source=infoq&utm_medium=feed&utm_term=global","date":"2026-02-02 11:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_776188f5.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"InfoQ","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":14,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_7c5bebcf","title":"大模型网关：大模型时代的智能交通枢纽｜得物技术","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxNTE3ODU0NA==&mid=2247542831&idx=1&sn=bdeb52cfadee2da4c47ce9e9fc3df7bc","date":"2026-02-02 10:30:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_7c5bebcf.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"得物技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":22,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_3f7f1e77","title":"谷歌 AI 掌门人、诺奖得主 Demis：AGI 需要打破“金鱼记忆”，而谷歌无论泡沫破裂与否都将是赢家","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247827870&idx=3&sn=657ef99dd56f72bde1c86b0cb32954b6","date":"2026-02-02 10:20:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_3f7f1e77.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":29,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_f061997f","title":"9999 元的 iPhone 16 PM 连“2+2”都算不对？排查 3 天以为是自己菜，最终发现是硬件 Bug","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247827870&idx=2&sn=5bb5851e120dfb04ad9cae70b04930fa","date":"2026-02-02 10:20:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_f061997f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":13,"score":84},{"id":"RAW_ea35dfb4","title":"退隐 3 年后回归，周末写的 AI 一夜刷屏、一周拿下 10 万 Star 增速超 Linux，Clawdbot 之父首次长谈：如今几乎不看自己发布的代码","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzMDY1NDgyOQ==&mid=2247827870&idx=1&sn=3a2d4e170c491fcc462373b82704b762","date":"2026-02-02 10:20:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ea35dfb4.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"CSDN","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":99,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_ea7e7995","title":"淘天集团自营技术运营算法团队 4 年 2 次荣膺 INFORMS“杰出实践奖”决选荣誉：以策略正则化突破 DRL 在库存管理中的落地瓶颈","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxNDEwNjk5OQ==&mid=2650542682&idx=1&sn=4a56846c13628675c01337e79b01d614","date":"2026-02-02 09:05:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_ea7e7995.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"大淘宝技术","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":26,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_8fbe16d8","title":"多维创新打造强泛化智能体模型，LongCat-Flash-Thinking-2601 技术报告发布","link":"https://tech.meituan.com/2026/02/02/longcat-flash-thinking-2601-techreport.html","date":"2026-02-02 00:00:00","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_8fbe16d8.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Programming_Technology","sourceName":"美团技术团队","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":19,"score":91},{"id":"RAW_9edf25b9","title":"2026-02-06 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-06-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-06 08:48:50","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_9edf25b9.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":77,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_23158235","title":"[AINews] OpenAI 与 Anthropic 开战：Claude Opus 4.6 对决 GPT 5.3 Codex","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-openai-and-anthropic-go-to","date":"2026-02-06 04:10:33","oneSentenceSummary":"本报告分析了在 GPT-5.3-Codex 和 Claude Opus 4.6 同步发布后，OpenAI 与 Anthropic 之间的激烈竞争，重点介绍了向智能体工作流和硬件优化效率的转变。","summary":"本文深入探讨了由 OpenAI 和 Anthropic 同步发布旗舰编程模型引发的“AI 大战”。文章对比了 Anthropic 在公关上的成功（通过自主智能体团队构建净室 C 编译器来展示）与 OpenAI 对性能、速度以及针对 GB200-NVL72 平台的硬件协同设计的关注。除了模型更新，报告还探讨了行业从简单的 LLM 框架向强制执行规划和验证的“严格治理框架（harnesses）”的转变。此外，报告总结了多智能体系统（SALE 和 Agent Primitives）的前沿研究，并提供数据表明 AI 智能体目前占 GitHub 公开提交量的 4%，预示着软件开发劳动力模式的根本性转变。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_23158235.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":31,"score":90},{"id":"RAW_741975b6","title":"操控万亿参数模型、生产环境中的 Token 级 PII、超越 SAE —— Goodfire AI 的 Myra Deng 与 Mark Bissell","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/goodfire","date":"2026-02-05 20:45:01","oneSentenceSummary":"本文探讨了 Goodfire AI 的使命，即推动机械可解释性从研究实验室走向生产基础设施，在尖端规模上实现精准的模型操控和可靠的安全控制。","summary":"访谈记录了在获得 1.5 亿美元 B 轮融资后，与 Goodfire AI 领导层进行的深入技术讨论。内容详述了他们如何从“事后”机械可解释性研究转向构建“可操作”的生产工作流。核心议题包括在乐天（Rakuten）部署稀疏自编码器（SAEs）和探针进行实时 PII 检测、SAE 特征与原始激活分类器之间的权衡，以及操控 Kimi K2 等万亿参数模型的能力。对话强调了基于可解释性的护栏相较于 LLM-as-a-judge 方法具有更低的延迟和更高的效率。此外，还引入了“有意图的模型设计”概念，即在训练阶段利用可解释性来缓解阿谀奉承（sycophancy）和奖励黑客（reward hacking）等问题，超越了传统微调和 RLHF 的暴力限制。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_741975b6.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":58,"score":88},{"id":"RAW_2744842f","title":"2026-02-05 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-05-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-05 08:48:51","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_2744842f.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":73,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_d16bfa6f","title":"[AINews] ElevenLabs 以 110 亿美元估值完成 5 亿美元 D 轮融资，Cerebras 以 230 亿美元估值完成 10 亿美元 H 轮融资，从 Vibe Coding 转向智能体工程 (Agentic Engineering)","link":"https://www.latent.space/p/ainews-elevenlabs-500m-series-d-at","date":"2026-02-05 08:26:43","oneSentenceSummary":"这份全面的 AI 新闻综述重点介绍了 ElevenLabs 和 Cerebras 的巨额融资、向“智能体工程”的转型，以及 Gemini 3、VS Code 智能体和 Qwen3 等开源模型的重大更新。","summary":"报告涵盖了 AI 行业的关键时刻，ElevenLabs 和 Cerebras 以数十亿美元的估值跻身“十角兽”行列。一个主要主题是 AI 辅助开发的演进，在 VS Code 新的 Agent Sessions 和 GitHub Copilot 集成多种模型的支持下，从“Vibe Coding”转向“智能体工程”。技术里程碑包括 GPT-5.2 High 的 6.6 小时任务跨度、高效 Qwen3-Coder-Next MoE 模型的发布，以及 ACE-Step 1.5 在实时音频生成方面的进展。此外，文章还详细介绍了 NVIDIA GB200 的基础设施收益以及机器人研究中“世界动作模型” (World Action Models) 的出现。","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_d16bfa6f.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"Latent Space","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":32,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_585f577d","title":"今年都在求「健康福」，我测完这个 AI 后决定直接转发家庭群","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654064?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-04 17:00:28","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_585f577d.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":14,"score":86},{"id":"RAW_b57c3f8d","title":"Genie 3 引发游戏股暴跌，但游戏的真正灵魂 AI 永远得不到","link":"https://www.ifanr.com/1654197?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=","date":"2026-02-04 13:44:27","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_b57c3f8d.json","topicTag":"other","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"爱范儿","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":18,"score":87},{"id":"RAW_cf23725c","title":"2026-02-04 Hacker News Top Stories #","link":"https://supertechfans.com/cn/post/2026-02-04-HackerNews/","date":"2026-02-04 08:19:22","archive_path":"data/articles/2026/02/RAW_cf23725c.json","topicTag":"ai-llm","category":"Business_Tech","sourceName":"SuperTechFans","resourceType":"ARTICLE","readTime":68,"score":89},{"id":"RAW_0d2d4723","title":"产业之声 | CES 科技展：中美欧日韩的对比观察和产业趋势","link":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5NTg0NDE1Mw==&mid=2652627729&idx=1&sn=2f69c1efc1dcae6cd842cd7b142d4fe3","date"